thread.title: Blue Jays clinch AL East with 15-2 win over Orioles
thread.title_full: Blue Jays clinch AL East with 15-2 win over Orioles

title: Blue Jays clinch AL East with 15-2 win over Orioles
text:
> Sports Blue Jays clinch AL East with 15-2 win over Orioles Toronto Blue Jays' Josh Donaldson doubles in front of Baltimore Orioles catcher Steve Clevenger and home plate umpire Kerwin Danley in the fifth inning in the first baseball game of a doubleheader, Wednesday, Sept. 30, 2015, in Baltimore. Ben Revere scored on the play. (AP Photo/Patrick Semansky) Search Help
